Bachelor of Computer Applications - BCA

Bachelor of Computer Application (B.C.A) is a three year, six semester degree programme.

The department has separate high end lab with net facility. The faculty are well experienced and committed to impart knowledge as per the needs of the course. The students are well placed in reputed IT industries all over the world.

The students can also pursue higher education after completion of the course.

Special Features

The department is equipped with many Journals/Magazines and the students have access to a wide variety of Online content. Placement initiatives are taken by the Students Service Centre of our college. The college provides the necessary training for students to face interviews and other exams for successful placements in IT corporates. The students will have workshops and seminars as part of their association activates which will be conducted by reputed IT Firms.

INTERNSHIP

The students are assigned small projects during the course duration. In the final semester the students will have to do a main project as per the university norms. The students are also taken for Industrial visits.

Courses Content

  Programming Languages
